#: ../../../reference/conanfile/tools.rst:6
msgid "Tools are all things that can be imported and used in Conan recipes."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/conanfile/tools.rst:10
msgid ""
"This is the current design for Conan 2.0, and these will be the supported "
"tools. Only the tools documented in this section will be available in Conan "
"2.0."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/conanfile/tools.rst:13
msgid ""
"Some of the features used in this section are still **under development**, "
"while they are recommended and usable and we will try not to break them in "
"future releases, some breaking changes might still happen if necessary to "
"prepare for the *Conan 2.0 release*."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/conanfile/tools.rst:17
msgid ""
"Most of the utilities defined in \"conan.tools\" will require very soon to "
"define both the \"host\" and \"build\" profiles. It is very recommended to "
"start defining both profiles immediately to avoid future breaking. "
"Furthermore, some features, like trying to cross-compile might not work at "
"all if the \"build\" profile is not provided."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/conanfile/tools.rst:22
msgid "The import path is always like:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/conanfile/tools.rst:24
msgid ""
"from conan.tools.cmake import CMakeToolchain, CMakeDeps, CMake\n"
"from conan.tools.microsoft import MSBuildToolchain, MSBuildDeps, MSBuild"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/conanfile/tools.rst:30
msgid "The main guidelines are:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/conanfile/tools.rst:32
msgid ""
"Imports must be in the form ``from conan.tools.xxx import yyy``, or ``from "
"conan.tools import xxx``. Do not use ``from conan import tools`` nor ``from "
"conan.tools.xxx.yyy import zzz``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/conanfile/tools.rst:34
msgid ""
"Everything that recipes can use belong to ``from conan.tools``. Any other "
"import is private implementation and shouldn't be used in recipes (except "
"``from conan import ConanFile`` and ``from conan.errors``)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/conanfile/tools.rst:36
msgid ""
"Only documented tools with explicitly documented imports can be used in "
"recipes. Do not use any other import not found in this section of the "
"documentation, even if they are in the ``from conan.tools`` namespace."
msgstr ""

